:R-HSA-549127  a            owl:NamedIndividual , obo:GO_0015837 ;
        rdfs:comment        "The organic cation transporters comprise three SLC22 members, OCT1-3. They can transport a wide range of organic cations including weak bases. All transport by OCTs is electrogenic, sodium-independent and bidirectional. Two further organic cation transporters mediate transport of ergothioneine and carnitine (Koepsell H and Endou H, 2004)." ;
        rdfs:label          "Organic cation transport" ;
        dc:contributor      "Reviewed: D'Eustachio, Peter, 2025-08-12" , "Edited: Jassal, Bijay, 2010-03-17" , "GOC:reactome_curators" , "Reviewed: He, L, 2010-05-10" , "Authored: Jassal, Bijay, 2010-03-17" ;
        dc:date             "2026-06-29" ;
        pav:providedBy      "https://reactome.org" ;
